{"tid":1249982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[應付民意] 游擊戰係咪更加要隱藏抗爭者身份？","createTime":"2019-06-22T01:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T13:12:13.000Z","uid":78769,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e3b43e2ecb923918e0e646041d1dd1b4a051d524","tid":1249982,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T01:43:42.000Z","msg":"見到有人話游擊佔領會影響民生，拖累民意，咁決定要打游擊（e.g.流動佔領）嘅話，應唔應該要隱藏抗爭者身份，扮到同平民一樣？<br />\n<br />\n純粹靠<span style=\"color: red;\">人流量</span>作為手段，強調靈活性，唔去陣地式佔領。即係話唔好比人認得到你哋係示威者，咁如果有人想搵人屌都冇辦法。"},{"pid":"c431393aaf16d5762dab06ddc9422e5e742a7390","tid":1249982,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T01:52:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b47f96d980557bbaa4e651b0afb0ced3c74052ac","tid":1249982,"uid":224323,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T01:59:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一入場區就戴口罩，<br />\n<br />\n一離場區就除口罩。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">離遠小小，小心天眼，小心電子消費。</span>"},{"pid":"4927f7ed3f3b145f7d4036f54b9e1d53655bc4ce","tid":1249982,"uid":52477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b47f96d980557bbaa4e651b0afb0ced3c74052ac","tid":1249982,"uid":224323,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T01:59:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一入場區就戴口罩，<br />\n<br />\n一離場區就除口罩。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">離遠小小，小心天眼，小心電子消費。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n場區以外嘅天眼係緊接住架<br />\n離到好撚遠先好除"},{"pid":"0c501672d015c47b61e3e1e86e8ede1a659194dc","tid":1249982,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T02:02:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\